happy wedding is 2016 indian malayalam romantic comedy-drama film directed by debutante omar lulu . starring sharafudheen , soubin shahir , siju wilson , and justin john in the lead roles , the film is jointly produced by eros international and nazir ali under his banner ozone productions . it narrates the story of an engineering graduate ( wilson ) as he contemplates marriage on his mother 's insistence . music by arun muraleedharan principal photography which began in kochi in november 2015 ended in march 2016 . other shooting locations were thrissur and chalakudy . some parts of the film were also shot in royal college of engineering and technology , akkikavu , thrissur . the film was released on 20 may 2016 .